Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.72,0:00:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和海火子為了封印通向魔界之門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.47,0:00:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前往天部界尋求"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"為千年一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.60,0:00:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當劍龍降臨大地時才會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,於是 這個時刻來臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在從天而降的劍龍生下白龍的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.22,0:00:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我得到了它的淚水化成的"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.36,0:00:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 閻羅王竟將"劍龍之勾玉"一刀兩斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.60,0:00:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我們就在沒有得到"劍龍之勾玉"的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回神部界去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.76,0:01:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(200,250)}—\h沒有終結之時的物語\h—
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.68,0:01:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(250,1900)}永遠的傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡真的是創界山嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.74,0:01:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是靜得反常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.28,0:01:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.10,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是本少爺啊 你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.39,0:01:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.24,0:01:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.78,0:02:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是老虎啊是老虎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.97,0:02:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.41,0:02:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你從哪來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.70,0:02:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子 大家在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.70,0:02:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是問古拿瑪 武一郎大叔他們啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.70,0:02:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神部七龍神被…變成石頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.57,0:02:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"在渡體內?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍之一族的長老是這樣說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.78,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是令人似懂非懂的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.45,0:02:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是說能拯救神部界的只有渡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:02:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閻羅王真是可怕的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.96,0:03:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他放出的邪惡的能量將神部七龍神變成了石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼魔界那些傢伙不一口氣進攻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.11,0:03:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能是他們知道我們沒有拿到"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.12,0:03:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就掉以輕心按兵不動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.65,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是說他們大意的現在正是大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.51,0:03:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對啊 因為渡正持有"劍龍之勾玉"呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.59,0:03:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然有…但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.26,0:03:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有時間考慮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.09,0:03:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快前往大門的所在地吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們也想一起去 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別太勉強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家要去哪裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.20,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是去玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也要加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 你得留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真無聊啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是救世主大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.73,0:04:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代替我 把這個帶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.81,0:04:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 虎王 海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由我們來保護神部界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.17,0:04:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.39,0:05:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什麼在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.79,0:05:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於出現了 怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.28,0:05:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水…是水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大門在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.90,0:05:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是連接魔界與神部界的大門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.58,0:05:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.46,0:05:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吼鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.45,0:06:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 交給本少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼會有那麼堅硬的盔甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍對那傢伙是無效的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.15,0:06:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我引開它注意力的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們倆從上方攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.92,0:07:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.25,0:07:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧 坐上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.46,0:07:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有點嗆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和海火子待在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看啊 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.78,0:08:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.06,0:08:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快給它最後一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.65,0:08:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能殺了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它可是魔界的怪物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它已經不能戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快趁現在將魔界之門…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.09,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火子 你受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這點小傷算不了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起這個 還是快把門…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.26,0:09:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剩下的就交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子 帶海火子回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.15,0:09:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人的心中寄宿著魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界之人支配著魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而人又被魔鬼所支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連接魔界與神部界的大門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是在這下面正在開啟的水之門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連通魔界的這些水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作為絕對屏障的神聖之水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.62,0:10:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原本是為了阻擋我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.38,0:10:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但現在卻變成了魔界的生命之海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.99,0:10:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神部界之人不能碰觸這些水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更別說是普通的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,否則肉體就會立刻腐爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,血液也會沸騰起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閻羅王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去"劍龍之勾玉"的你們注定要失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.82,0:10:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡的體內有"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"正是救世主的印證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.55,0:10:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果取出"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.87,0:11:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並放到那塊石板上後 你認為會怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡瞬間就被封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.65,0:11:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論是神部界之人還是魔界之人都永遠不能進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.97,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也別想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.13,0:11:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你將永遠長眠於此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惡魔神大暗黑龍的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.09,0:11:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大暗黑龍!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.85,0:11:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不久大暗黑龍就要從這裡飛脫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.54,0:11:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再也沒有人能夠阻止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神部界的滅亡之時已經來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.16,0:11:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界的生命之海正在為大暗黑龍的復活尋求祭品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是救世主的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,廢話少說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.55,0:12:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賭上魔界和神的世界的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以劍來場一對一的勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看不清他的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.40,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要把你那些救世主的印記一個個的奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.23,0:13:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.95,0:13:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來只剩下救世主的印證"劍龍之勾玉"了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.02,0:13:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只留下那個做你的陪葬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我從沒認為自己是什麼救世主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.34,0:13:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.17,0:13:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要殺死拚命求生的生物!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.85,0:14:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.60,0:14:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能對受苦的人們見死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是為了保護那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在就作為救世主戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就乖乖的作為救世主受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.25,0:14:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.02,0:15:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼…為什麼非得戰鬥不可啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.25,0:15:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為那是你的…宿命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.58,0:15:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.73,0:16:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已經得到"劍龍之勾玉"了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.91,0:16:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.59,0:16:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使如此…也是你們…輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 把"劍龍之勾玉"交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.68,0:17:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由本少爺跳下去完成封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.77,0:17:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼做的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本少爺體內還留著魔界的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.70,0:17:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡做不了 但本少爺能做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 快乘白龍馬逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王已經不是魔界的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這件事沒人去做是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.22,0:17:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就由我去做 這是我的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡作為救世主的使命已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回自己的世界去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還沒完成啊 這是最後的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.86,0:17:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.20,0:17:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 兩個人一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果騎著這傢伙 說不定會稍微緩解魔界的毒素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.28,0:17:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結果到最後還是和渡一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.84,0:18:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為本少爺和渡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.45,0:18:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 你先騎上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.51,0:18:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本少爺一定會回去的 相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啊 虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 白龍馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.00,0:18:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.90,0:20:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.65,0:20:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,母后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.40,0:21:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使擁有神部七龍神的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不能打碎或融化這些冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.98,0:21:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王就在這些冰下沉睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信他說的"一定會回去"的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.50,0:21:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然創界山迎來永久的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.15,0:21:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但不知為何卻不能從心底高興起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.98,0:21:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去"劍龍之勾玉"的渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經不再是救世主了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 渡就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.77,0:21:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山已經得到了永遠的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的使命也完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.39,0:21:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以後不會再來創界山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.75,0:21:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 你以後不會再來玩了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.55,0:21:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將渡和我們連接在一起的羈絆只有戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.85,0:21:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主並不是只為了和魔界之人戰鬥才誕生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.95,0:22:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主是為了給予活在痛苦中的人們以喜悅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.44,0:22:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給予仇恨中的人們慈愛才誕生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.00,0:22:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而渡也出色的完成了這項使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡和我們在一起的這段日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.67,0:22:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將作為傳說流傳下去 永遠的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.99,0:22:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"無盡"正是由渡產生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.47,0:22:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍神丸 謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.91,0:22:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.75,0:22:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會忘記和大家在一起的這"永遠的時刻"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.80,0:22:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.49,0:22:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還要再來啊 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.05,0:22:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等著你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.75,0:22:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還要再和老虎一起玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.50,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.50,0:23:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.42,0:23:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就這樣 我完成了救世主的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.58,0:23:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回到自己的世界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.40,0:23:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,季節由夏到冬 然後又變到春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.00,0:23:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我內心的"永遠的時刻"似乎就那樣停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.60,0:23:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王究竟回到創界山了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在也無法知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.35,0:23:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我所能做到的 只有抱著這樣的信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.33,0:23:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白龍馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.83,0:25:57.81,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}耳をふさいでも 聞こえていたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.77,0:26:04.98,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}時の砂が落ちる音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.11,0:26:13.32,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}黃昏に金の雲を残して
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.91,0:26:20.12,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}沈む夕陽をせつなく見る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.33,0:26:32.05,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}Adieu 悲しみの 夜は來るけれど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.34,0:26:36.10,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}淚 見せない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.39,0:26:39.85,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}永遠の扉を
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.13,0:26:51.32,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}開けば始まる 終わりなき時の物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.61,0:26:55.28,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}出逢いは一瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.49,0:26:59.08,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}でも胸に Memory
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.54,0:27:10.84,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,350)}君の熱さを忘れないよ Forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.83,0:25:57.81,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}即使堵上耳朵也能聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.77,0:26:04.98,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}沙漏漏下的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.11,0:26:13.32,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}黃昏時只殘留金色的雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.91,0:26:20.12,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}難過的看著夕陽落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.33,0:26:32.05,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}Adieu 悲傷的夜晚到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.34,0:26:36.10,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}卻不讓你看見淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.39,0:26:39.85,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}只要開啟永遠的門扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.13,0:26:51.32,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}永恆的傳說就會開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.61,0:26:55.28,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}雖然只有瞬間的邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.49,0:26:59.08,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}但胸中的 Memory
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.54,0:27:10.84,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,350)}不會忘記你的熱情 Forever
